entries.femaleVariant: Yo, don't forget, we're playin' tonight.
Like I forgot! Game's the only reason I get out of bed in the mornin', choom.
We win tonight, we're goin' somewhere that'll really get you up, heh heh.
Nope, not for me. I'm here for the poker, that's it.
C'mon. Kid's on the way whether I like it or not.
